SUMMARY:Board Game Night
DESCRIPTION:Central PA Game Club\nCome join us at Lazarus Games for board 
 game night! Meet new people and bring your friends. We are still building 
 our collection of games for the store and have limited options\, so bring 
 along any you might want to play.
