DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260404T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260404T203000
SUMMARY:Metropolitan Mount Carmel Gamers Guild Session
DESCRIPTION:Central PA Game Club\nWe are a tabletop RPG group. We currentl
 y have 2 groups running\; one is playing Pathfinder (a take on D&D 3.5 rul
 es) and the other group is playing Alternity (a space adventure setting). 
 We are always looking for players of all experiences. If you have the will
  to play we can teach you how. More info about the group can also be found
  on our Facebook page @ facebook.com/groups/mmcgg\n\nWe usually have betwe
 en 17 and 20 people attending each session. *WE DO NOT USUALLY CANCEL SESS
 IONS. IF IT IS LISTED ON THE CALENDER THEN IT IS HAPPENING. WE WILL SPECIF
 ICALLY POST IF A SESSION IS CANCELED.\n\nOur next gaming session will take
  place at 3 pm at the Library. You're welcome to join us. We have been goi
 ng back and forth between ordering food and potluck so it's best to check 
 our Facebook page for the latest info (facebook.com/groups/mmcgg). If the 
 front door is not open when you arrive\, please call 570-863-9028 to gain 
 entry. If you know of other people looking to join\, please share this wit
 h them or call the previous phone number to let us know they are coming.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/centralpagameclub/events/313799731/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260316T181420Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260316T181420Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
